  Printer, TS 1000 + RamPack, ZX Spectrum + Interfaccia 1 e Microdrive,
  ZX Spectrum +, TS 2068, Zx Spectrum 128K, ZX Spectrum +2,
  ZX Spectrum +3,QL (con la collaborazione di Tiziano).
- Commodore Pet 4008
- Collezione home computer Commodore: VIC20, C64 + Floppy 1541, C64G,
  C64C, Amiga 500, Amiga 600
- Commodore 128, Amiga 1200 tower elbox 68060 + expander Yamaha,
  Commodore CDTV, Cubo CD32 -clone di Amiga CD32-, calcolatrici
  Commodore e Sinclair (a cura di Davide 'Zaxxon' Bressanini)
- Workstation Sun: SparcStation 1, SparcStation 1+, SparcStation 2,
  SparcStation LX, SparcStation IPX, SparcStation IPC, SparcStation 10,
  Sun Station ELC, SparcStation Voyager, SparcStation 20,
  SparcStation 5, SUN X/Terminal 1, SparcStation Classic X, SparcStation
  Ultra 1, SparcStation 4, SparcStation Ultra 5 (a cura di Gianni BBK
  Zamperini)
- CIP03, un clone rumeno dello ZX Spectrum e Olivetti Prodest PC128s
  (a cura di Stefano -flydream-)
- Cloni Sinclair Spectrum: Pentagon 128K, GrandRomMax 128K, Spectrum
